2022 - Thank you to the wonderful collaborators, clients, friends, and artists who trusted me this year – to photograph on film, with your special moments, and to execute a creative vision. For me, it was a year of decisions, growth, and taking stock of where I want to go. There were many exciting moments- attending NYFW, and others that are still to be released - stay tuned for 2023! I appreciate you all for sticking with me and your kind comments and support. And wishing you all a very happy New Year to come! 💫
